 Hospital]]'' actor||born in Australia||naturalized U.S. citizen<!--IMDB ref--> |- |[[Portia de Rossi]]||1973–|| ''[[Ally McBeal]]'' actress and wife of [[Ellen DeGeneres]]||born in Australia||naturalized U.S. citizen |- |[[Kristen Stewart]]||1990–||actress||mother is Australian||born in the U.S. |- |[[Breanna Yde]]||2003–||actress||Australian Born American Actress||Born in Sydney, New South Wales |}
