{{Infobox Political post |post = First Lady |body = Maryland |insignia = Seal of Maryland (reverse).svg |insigniacaption = Seal of the State of Maryland |insigniasize = 150px |style = |image = Yumi Hogan at Bosom Buddies Ball - 2018 (24855244737) (cropped).jpg{{!}}border |incumbent = [[Yumi Hogan]] |incumbentsince = January 21, 2015 |termlength = |residence = [[Government House (Maryland)|Government House]] |formation = {{start date and age|1777|3|21}} |inaugural = Ann Jennings Johnson |salary = |website = [http://governor.maryland.gov/firstlady/ Official website] }} The spouse of the [[Governor of Maryland]] is given an honorary position, styled as [[First Lady]] or First Gentleman of the State of [[Maryland]]. To date there have been no female governors of the State of Maryland, and all First Spouses have been First Ladies.
